" data-image-caption="&lt;p>;Virtual Zeven&lt;/p>;
" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/virtual_zeven_image.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/virtual_zeven_image.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/virtual_zeven_image.jpg?resize=1100%2C619&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-112774" data-recalc-dims="1"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：脸书<br>© www.virtualzeven.com</figcaption></figure><p> Virtual Zeven 是泰国 VTuber <strong>HØRI 07</strong>根据她过去属于各种机构和团体的经验，于 2023 年（令和 5 年）成立的 VTuber 机构。</p><p>基于“ <em>VTuber不必只存在于屏幕上</em>”的理念，我们的目标是让VTuber人才成为泰国媒体行业更容易接受的娱乐形式。</p><p>根据<a href="https://p2y.jp/survey-finds-algorhythm-project-making-great-strides-in-thailand-vtuber-industry/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="本站 1 月 9 日文章">该网站 1 月 9 日文章</a>中发表的调查结果，它似乎是泰国第六受欢迎的。</p><p></p><h2 id="outline__2" class="wp-block-heading">出道MV </h2><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="น่ารักยกกำลัง 2 (双重伤害) - SW33TH34RT [官方MV]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uAfVT8hsZak?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[TEASER} SW33TH34RT 项目 l 虚拟 Zeven" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_1akVb-z4ds?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><h2 id="outline__3" class="wp-block-heading"> SUMM3R（夏季） </h2><figure class="wp-block-imag