uot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="houshou_marine_surpassed_kizuna_ai_youtube_subscribers_for_the_first_time_in_japanese_vtuber_history" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/houshou_marine_surpassed_kizuna_ai_youtube_subscribers_for_the_first_time_in_japanese_vtuber_history.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/houshou_marine_surpassed_kizuna_ai_youtube_subscribers_for_the_first_time_in_japanese_vtuber_history.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/houshou_marine_surpassed_kizuna_ai_youtube_subscribers_for_the_first_time_in_japanese_vtuber_history.png?resize=1100%2C619&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-111574" data-recalc-dims="1"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：YouTube<br> © 2016 COVER 公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>截至1月20日，filian（隶属于Mythic Talent）是全球YouTube官方频道视频观看次数最多的VTuber艺人，观看次数约为938,109,419次。 Hosho Marine 的总浏览量仅次于 filian，但总浏览量正在以每周 9 至 1000 万次的速度累积，与 filian 的差距正在迅速缩小。因此，如果维持目前的趋势， Marin Hosho 很有可能成为 YouTube 官方频道全球视频总观看次数最高的 VTuber 达人。</p><p> 1 月 10 日，Hosho Marine 订阅用户数达到 301 万。据证实，日本VTuber人才史上首次频道订阅人数超过了Kizuna AI（无限期停播/Kizuna AI Co., Ltd.）。 </p><p></p><div class="cprfl65b1ac49575ce" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
